# Build artifacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/node_modules/

# Version control and tooling
.git/
.github/
.vs/
.agents/

# Docs (keep README.md out of image to reduce context; not needed at runtime)
**/*.md
!README.md

# SQLite databases (mounted as a volume at runtime)
**/database.sqlite*

# Test projects (not needed in the Docker build context)
Snappass.NET.UnitTest/
Snappass.NET.IntegrationTest/
